---
title: Turkey Kofta Tray Bake with Orzo and Lemony Hummus Sauce
description: 2023 is the year of the tray bake! Layers of zucchini, peppers and shawarma-spiced koftas get baked to perfection, then piled on top of orzo and finished with lemony garlic-hummus sauce.
